gText_Birch_Welcome::
	.string "Hi there, Etienne! It's so good to see\n"
    .string "you!\p"
    .string "Your friends have been talking about\n"
    .string "you a lot lately.\p"
    .string "They've been working hard on something\n"
    .string "special just for you!\p"
    .string "Oh and by the way, happy birthday!\p"
    .string "Your friends wanted to make this game\n"
    .string "extra exciting and enjoyable for a\l"
    .string "Pokémon veteran like you.\p"
    .string "We've made a few changes to spice\n"
    .string "things up and keep you on your toes.\p"
    .string "So be sure to pay attention and\n"
    .string "explore every corner of the game\l"
    .string "to discover hidden surprises!\p"
    .string "But before we dive in, let's skip the\n"
    .string "usual introduction about this world\l"
    .string "inhabited by creatures called POKéMON.\p"
    .string "I'm sure you're already familiar with\n"
    .string "all of that. So let's jump right in!\p"
    .string "Oh, wait! Usually, you would need to\n"
    .string "choose your gender and name. Don't\l"
    .string "worry: we've got that covered too.\p"
    .string "$"

gText_Birch_AreYouReady::
	.string "All right, are you ready?\p"
	.string "Your very own adventure is about\n"
	.string "to unfold.\p"
	.string "Take courage, and leap into the\n"
	.string "world of POKéMON where dreams,\l"
	.string "adventure, and friendships await!\p"
	.string "Well, I'll be expecting you later.\n"
	.string "Come see me in my POKéMON LAB.\p"
	.string "$"
